The only other RAs that everyone remembers are the &quot;jokes&quot; - Tundra especially seems to have a hilarious reputation, and I don't even know what it does <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
The parry-thing. I dind't notice really. I guess I didn't plan on speccing into Parry until much later, or somethin'. No, seriously, I was a newbie. Anyhow, I had Evade1 and the fantastic Twin Return (I actually recall using that while levelling <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  )<br>
<br>
Survivability in RvR is a class type/realm balance thing, and is based on many factors. When fighting 2 oponents, I'd rather be a merc than anything else (for the purposes of fun). Let's hope the RvR expansion gives something to us dimwitted bommy-knocker classes. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :D --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/happy.gif ALT=":D"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
